Nazir Tanbouli (a mụrụ n'afọ 1971) bụ onye Ijipt amụrụ na-ese ihe
A mụrụ ya ma zụlite ya na Alexandria, Ijipt ma gụọ akwụkwọ na Mahadum nke Alexandria Faculty of Fine Arts
Nwanne nna ya bụ onye na-ese ihe bụ Ibrahim El-Tanbouli (b
1954) na nwanne nna ya bụ onye na-ese ihe na onye Egyptologist Lotfy El-Tanbouli (1919 ruo 1982)
Ọ na-arụ ọrụ na eserese na eserese, ọkachasị  eserese mural.

A mụrụ ya n'ezinụlọ ndị na-ese ihe, gụnyere onye na-ese foto na Egyptologist Lotfy El Tanbouli Nazir Tanbouli e nyere ya 1993 Grand Drawing Prize na National Salon of Youth, Egypt ma sonye na Cairo Bienniale na ọtụtụ ihe ngosi ndị ọzọ na Egypt na mba ofesi
Ọ nọrọ ọtụtụ afọ naanị na eserese mural
Ọ biri ọtụtụ afọ na Nottingham ebe ọ bụ onye na-ese ihe na onye nkuzi na-arụsi ọrụ ike, wee malite igosi ihe na Europe. N'afọ 2007 ọ kwagara London ebe ọ bi ma na-arụ ọrụ.
N'afọ 2010 ọ gụsịrị MA na Fine Art (Printmaking) na Camberwell College of Arts
O jikọtara aka guzobe oghere Studio 75, nke na-emepụta ọrụ ma na-akwado ihe ngosi
Tanbouli enwetala onyinye dị mkpa site na Kansụl nka nke England yana ntọala onwe onye, a na-ejikwa ọrụ ya na nchịkọta ọha na eze na Ijipt na ọtụtụ nchịkọta onwe na UK
